jpg 2560w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop3-300x224.jpg 300w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop3-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop3-768x574.jpg 768w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop3-1536x1147.jpg 1536w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop3-2048x1530.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"ロッテマート_shop4\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1912\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3124\" srcset=\"https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-300x224.jpg 300w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-768x574.jpg 768w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-1536x1147.jpg 1536w, https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/LM_shop4-2048x1530.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>営業時間：8：00～22：00<br />\n定休日：テト休み<br />\nクレジットカード：OK<br />\n住所：54 Lieu Giai（ロッテセンターハノイ 地下1階）／229 Tay Son （Mipec Tower内）／302 Cau Giay （Discovery Complex 地下1階）<br />\n<a href=\"http://lottemart.com.vn/he-thong/sieu-thi-lotte-mart-ha-noi-center/\">http://lottemart.com.vn/he-thong/sieu-thi-lotte-mart-ha-noi-center/</a></p>\n\n\n<div style=\"background-color: #f0f8ff; border: 2px solid #1e90ff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;\">\n<h3 style=\"color: #1e90ff; margin-top: 0;\">ベトナムで働くことに興味はありませんか？</h3>\n<p>キャリアリンクアジアでは、ベトナム・ハノイの日系企業の求人を多数掲載しています。現地での生活に慣れてきたら、ベトナムで働くという選択肢も検討してみてはいかがでしょうか。</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/vietnam/job/list\" style=\"color: #1e90ff;\">▶ ベトナムの求人一覧を見る</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://kyujin.careerlink.asia/jobseeker/register\" style=\"color: #1e90ff;\">▶ 無料会員登録はこちら</a></strong></p>\n</div>"}